createElement()
appendChild()	
removeChild()

******************************

create element()
is used to create any html element using the javascript 
for example

var h1 = document.createElement('h1')
h1.textContent="Hello"
h1.classList.add("headingCss")

appendChild()
is used to join the elements to the body of thw html
for example
documement.queryselector("body").appendChild(h1)

removeChild()
is use to remove the element using the javascript
document.querySelector("body").remove(h1)